# C source formatting for the Applications/*.app Mach-O wrappers.
# Apply with: xcrun clang-format -i <file>.c
# (clang-format ships in the Xcode toolchain; reachable via xcrun.)
---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 4
TabWidth: 4
UseTab: Never
ColumnLimit: 75
BreakBeforeBraces: Linux
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align
PointerAlignment: Right
SpaceAfterCStyleCast: false
...
